
  Azumarill    Water Type Pokémon

  It lives in water virtually 
  all day long.  Its body color 
  and pattern act as camouflage 
  that makes it tough for enemies 
  to spot in water. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Azurill ► Marill ► Azumarill

